@ENDNODE

@NODE "Quiet" "Part 11 - The RENAME & RELABEL Commands - The QUIET Option"

@{B}@{U}The Rename QUIET Option@{UU} V2+ only@{UB}

Using the QUIET option for Rename will suppress the display of file names
when multiple renames are made. Thus you could use:-

  > RENAME df1:dir-1/File#? df1:dir-2/ QUIET

